{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "獵場", "storyInfo": "因為刺殺恩希歐迪斯未遂，危急時刻，莫希選擇了跳崖。\n而恩希歐迪斯對於這一切似乎毫不驚訝。大典即將開始。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來的行動準備好了？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯大人......！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我可以問一個問題嗎？", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真少見，這是不是你頭一次提出問題？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......屬下僭越。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，若按照我們的計畫行事，事後追查起來，布朗陶家恐怕也將受到牽連。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬下......屬下只是擔心，如今諾希斯大人與布朗陶家結成同盟，若是布朗陶家遭發難，是否會對諾希斯大人的計畫不利......", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的問題我也考慮過，不過無妨，布朗陶家如何從來不是重點，這次機會十分難得，我不希望錯過。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也希望你能保全自己。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果真的出現最壞的情況，不需要考慮布朗陶家的問題。我瞭解恩希歐迪斯，只要你的證詞對他有利，他大概暫時不會動你。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時我會安排人手確保你的安全。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯大人！我......", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......怎麼了？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你有顧慮，計畫也可以換人執行。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不！請讓我來！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#3$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要是諾希斯大人的吩咐......", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫希在所不辭。", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "showall", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 3.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這下總算是把那些野獸全部解決了！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一兩個小子受了點傷，但沒什麼大礙......多虧了聖女大人！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有做什麼。是各位出色地證明了自己的勇武，想必耶拉岡德也會為祂的勇士們自豪。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您、您過獎了......！", "name": "年長的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人！", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你是......剛剛的......", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我。多謝聖女大人方才救了我一命。", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人！您剛剛確實是太冒險了！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但還是感謝您，感謝您救了這個混小子！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德的子民之間本就應當如此，不必言謝。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......聖女大人......", "name": "年輕的謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實是精彩的一箭。我還不曾聽聞聖女大人竟還有這樣的本領......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女原本就應有保護雪山民眾的能力，這並不是什麼值得特別提及的事。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您就是太謙虛了！方才的那一箭，我看完全能與我們謝拉格最善射的戰士比個高下！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#3$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人！阿克托斯大人，菈塔托絲大人！", "name": "謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不好了！", "name": "謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亂喊什麼？我們好得很。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是希瓦艾什家的人？怎麼，又出什麼事了，總不會是你們也遭到野獸襲擊，他恩希歐迪斯還要來找外援吧？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不是野獸！", "name": "謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那究竟是怎麼回事，不要吞吞吐吐，快說清楚！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！是恩希歐迪斯大人遭刺客襲擊！", "name": "謝拉格戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你說什麼？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯他被襲擊？竟有人敢在聖獵這樣的場合對他動手？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 