 {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡......你的那根手杖竟然能切開箭矢......", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在耍我嗎？！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要誤解。我並沒有要看輕你的意思。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做了很好的前期準備和規劃，但所有計劃都要面對實踐的考驗。紙面上的安排經常會被最直接的暴力打破。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望所有事情都能在交涉中體面解決，但我的同行者中就有具備此種暴力之人，歸功於她，我對這樣的人非常瞭解。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "謝拉格戰士？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底在說什麼？！", "name": "莫希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_255_1#7$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不願意露出真容嗎？難道是我看錯了？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "謝拉格戰士？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character",